               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa taklil “Book of the Marriage Ritual” (fols. 5ra-30vb) 
 -
                     Prayers on the clothes (fols. 5ra-10vb l.2) 
 - Prayers on the bride and
                     the bridegroom (fols. 10vb l.3-29ra l.5) 
 - Order to be read to the bride
                     and the bridegroom (fols. 29ra, l.5-30vb)
 II) Maṣḥafa qedar “Book of the
                     Jar” (fols. 31va-34vb, 36r-47r), incomplete</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
